MathIllustrator

MathIllustrator is a drag+drop tinymce LaTeX editor plugin

Prerequisites: None
Installation: Copy the folder into "moodle\lib\editor\tinymce\tiny_mce\<VERSION>\plugins" and name the folder "mathillustrator"
To display in moodle's tinymce editors, add "mathillustrator" to $params['plugins'] and the $params['theme_advanced_buttons<N>_add']
that you want in function get_init_params in "moodle\lib\editor\tinymce\lib.php"
Required: An HTML5 capable browser to view the MathIllustrator editor

Refer to the PDF documentation for more information: URL http://oohoo.biz/